\fBCommit Action Type\fR
T}:T{
.sp
The commit action type associated with the firmware activation event
T}
T{
.sp
\fBResult\fR
T}:T{
.sp
The result of the firmware activation event\&. The output shall be in the format: Pass or Failed + error code
T}
